Author: strangernumberone
Text: Feel this hard. Sometimes I'll go on MFP and plan all my meals out the day before. Thinking about what I'm having can make me crave it and then it's much more satisfying to eat when the time finally comes. And it helps me to know I have that next one planned to look forward to. Plus it helps me keep an eye on what vitamins I might be lacking or if my macros are all out of whack.
